⊢ prompt
  yield topic ≡ Explain why content-addressable storage matters for version control, in 3 sentences.

⊢ draft
  given prompt→topic
  yield text
  ∴∴ Write a first draft responding to «topic». Be concise but substantive.
  ⊨ text is not empty

⊢∘ refine × 3
  given draft→text
  yield text
  ∴∴ Improve «text». Make it clearer, more precise, and more compelling. Keep the same length (3 sentences). Return only the improved text, no commentary.
  ⊨ text is not empty

⊢ judge
  given draft→text
  given refine-3→text
  yield verdict
  ∴∴ Compare the original draft «text» with the refined version «text». Which is better and why? One paragraph.
  ⊨ verdict is not empty
